data.description: This spacious, well maintained home is your own personal, relaxing oasis away from your busy life!  You will look forward to coming home everyday to this 4 BR, 2.5 bath floor plan featuring a huge living room, formal dining, wonderful upgraded kitchen (refrigerator included) and generous bedrooms, all with walk-in closets and too many other great features to list!  It really gets fun when you head out back to your 15X34' fiberglass saltwater INGROUND POOL! Your loved ones will have a blast every weekend swimming and entertaining in this low maintenance, practically new pool!  There is also a new privacy fence around the large back yard and a metal outbuilding for extra storage. The central location is a quick commute to all the surrounding areas. Come discover all this home has to offer and don't miss this opportunity to LOVE YOUR HOME!  Call your agent to schedule a showing today!
